1
00:00:05,990 --> 00:00:11,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>According to witnesses, the victims were 
attacked by a large flock of eyeballs.</i></font>

2
00:00:27,950 --> 00:00:30,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sara's not coming today either?</i></font>

3
00:00:35,490 --> 00:00:36,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flum?</font>

4
00:00:39,320 --> 00:00:40,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flum?</font>

5
00:00:41,900 --> 00:00:42,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flum.</font>

6
00:00:44,810 --> 00:00:45,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flum?</font>

7
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:48,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flum?</font>

8
00:00:51,130 --> 00:00:52,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flum.</font>

9
00:00:58,120 --> 00:00:59,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flum?</font>

10
00:01:02,150 --> 00:01:04,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay, Flum?</font>

11
00:01:05,030 --> 00:01:06,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your face!</font>

12
00:01:06,190 --> 00:01:08,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm? Is there something on my face?</font>

13
00:01:09,020 --> 00:01:10,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you remember?</font>

14
00:01:11,150 --> 00:01:13,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were popping out eyeballs!</font>

15
00:01:13,900 --> 00:01:17,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What the heck? 
Did you have some kind of bad dream?</font>

16
00:01:18,360 --> 00:01:21,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You weirdo. Anyway, where's Milkit?</font>

17
00:01:22,390 --> 00:01:24,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't dream or hallucinate it!</font>

18
00:01:24,660 --> 00:01:26,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I clearly remember the smell and sounds!</font>

19
00:01:26,820 --> 00:01:29,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd turned into a monster, Ink!</font>

20
00:01:29,750 --> 00:01:33,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A monster? That's such 
a mean thing to say.</font>

21
00:01:33,540 --> 00:01:35,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I know what I saw!</font>

22
00:01:35,470 --> 00:01:38,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You weren't human!</font>

23
00:01:38,350 --> 00:01:39,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a human being!</font>

24
00:01:39,730 --> 00:01:44,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Church's tinkering must've 
turned you into something inhuman.</font>

25
00:01:45,460 --> 00:01:46,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why...</font>

26
00:01:47,700 --> 00:01:49,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why you don't have a heart.</font>

27
00:01:49,950 --> 00:01:50,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

28
00:01:50,970 --> 00:01:55,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. Now I know what 
that medicine you took was.</font>

29
00:01:55,810 --> 00:01:59,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was meant to suppress your powers.</font>

30
00:01:59,910 --> 00:02:03,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you stopped taking it and 
your powers went out of control,</font>

31
00:02:04,170 --> 00:02:05,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so those eyeballs appeared...</font>

32
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:09,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and went after all those people—
after Sara.</font>

33
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

34
00:02:12,850 --> 00:02:15,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, no...</font>

35
00:02:15,070 --> 00:02:17,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, no, no!</font>

36
00:02:17,950 --> 00:02:19,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't do that!</font>

37
00:02:20,160 --> 00:02:24,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love Sara and all of you!</font>

38
00:02:25,180 --> 00:02:29,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Ed, Jonny, and even 
Ottilie disappeared!</font>

39
00:02:29,900 --> 00:02:33,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now Eterna and Milkit are gone, too.</font>

40
00:02:34,830 --> 00:02:38,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't hurt my friends.</font>

41
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:40,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did, though!</font>

42
00:02:40,600 --> 00:02:43,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not what a friend does!</font>

43
00:02:45,630 --> 00:02:47,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I'm not a friend?</font>

44
00:02:50,780 --> 00:02:52,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I guess...</i></font>

45
00:02:53,070 --> 00:02:55,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm not allowed to be 
anywhere else but there.</i></font>

46
00:02:56,680 --> 00:03:00,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why... Why is this happening?</font>

47
00:03:06,070 --> 00:03:09,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get out here, Flum Apricot.</font>

48
00:04:40,010 --> 00:04:42,720
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}FLUM
DEIN</b></font>

49
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:45,010
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}DEIN AND FLUM</b></font>

50
00:04:47,150 --> 00:04:47,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dein!</font>

51
00:04:48,300 --> 00:04:50,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing here?</font>

52
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:52,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What else? A little guinea pig ran away,</font>

53
00:04:53,260 --> 00:04:55,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I came to take it back.</font>

54
00:04:55,610 --> 00:04:58,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, did you abduct Milkit too?</font>

55
00:04:58,820 --> 00:05:02,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The mummy girl's probably 
being tortured by the lady.</font>

56
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:04,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She'll be dead by now, I'd wager.</font>

57
00:05:05,430 --> 00:05:06,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"The lady"?</font>

58
00:05:06,940 --> 00:05:08,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't you figure it out?</font>

59
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:11,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean the mummy girl's former master,</font>

60
00:05:11,380 --> 00:05:13,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Satils Francois.</font>

61
00:05:14,070 --> 00:05:14,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

62
00:05:16,080 --> 00:05:18,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that why she reacted like that?</font>

63
00:05:20,110 --> 00:05:21,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa.</font>

64
00:05:22,100 --> 00:05:23,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come at me, Flum!</font>

65
00:05:24,100 --> 00:05:26,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want to save your friend, don't you?</font>

66
00:05:26,380 --> 00:05:28,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you can even call this freak a friend!</font>

67
00:05:35,030 --> 00:05:37,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like that murderous rage 
of yours. Bring it, Flum.</font>

68
00:05:43,410 --> 00:05:45,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dein! Where'd you go?</font>

69
00:05:45,990 --> 00:05:49,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm impressed you could 
keep up. Attagirl, Flum!</font>

70
00:05:49,960 --> 00:05:50,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dein!</font>

71
00:05:51,180 --> 00:05:53,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry to say this after 
you chased me so far,</font>

72
00:05:53,860 --> 00:05:57,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it's my job to get her 
where she needs to be.</font>

73
00:05:57,770 --> 00:06:00,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you want her, 
you'll have to fight your way out.</font>

74
00:06:00,050 --> 00:06:01,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dein!</font>

75
00:06:13,930 --> 00:06:15,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's with them?</i></font>

76
00:06:15,790 --> 00:06:19,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're working together 
and moving in sync.</i></font>

77
00:06:19,900 --> 00:06:20,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How?</i></font>

78
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:22,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Scan.</font>

79
00:06:22,900 --> 00:06:27,530
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}GODIN TORRES
TOTAL STATS: 2,482</b></font>

80
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:27,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Godin Torres, total stats of 2,482.</i></font>

81
00:06:27,860 --> 00:06:30,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>C-Rank? Is this one the leader, then?</i></font>

82
00:06:30,780 --> 00:06:32,620
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}GODIN TORRES
TOTAL STATS: 2,482</b></font>

83
00:06:32,620 --> 00:06:35,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh? Godin again?</i></font>

84
00:06:36,550 --> 00:06:40,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I know that one.
He's Grimmy, Dein's lackey.</i></font>

85
00:06:40,830 --> 00:06:41,830
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}GODIN TORRES
TOTAL STATS: 2,482</b></font>

86
00:06:42,450 --> 00:06:44,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why does it say Godin?</i></font>

87
00:06:44,840 --> 00:06:46,840
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}GODIN TORRES
TOTAL STATS: 2,482</b></font>

88
00:06:45,590 --> 00:06:47,840
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}GODIN TORRES
TOTAL STATS: 2,482</b></font>

89
00:06:45,740 --> 00:06:49,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They all have the same name and stats?</i></font>

90
00:06:47,840 --> 00:06:50,050
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}GODIN TORRES
TOTAL STATS: 2,482</b></font>

91
00:06:50,380 --> 00:06:52,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's going on here?</i></font>

92
00:06:51,090 --> 00:06:53,010
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}GODIN TORRES
TOTAL STATS: 2,482</b></font>

93
00:06:55,710 --> 00:06:59,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Something's up with their eyes. 
The Church must've meddled with them.</i></font>

94
00:07:00,110 --> 00:07:01,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Here he comes.</i></font>

95
00:07:05,420 --> 00:07:06,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reversal!</font>

96
00:07:10,620 --> 00:07:12,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One down!</font>

97
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:23,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Am I supposed to take all of them on...</font>

98
00:07:24,500 --> 00:07:26,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">all by myself?</font>

99
00:07:36,320 --> 00:07:37,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I...</i></font>

100
00:07:38,520 --> 00:07:39,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm not going down.</i></font>

101
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:44,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I refuse to die here!</font>

102
00:07:57,880 --> 00:07:59,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flum, use your prana!</font>

103
00:07:59,840 --> 00:08:02,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Strike the ground with your prana!</font>

104
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:10,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A technique that cuts up the enemy 
with a barrage of sword slashes:</i></font>

105
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:13,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Cavalier Arts: Prana Storm.</i></font>

106
00:08:21,420 --> 00:08:23,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay alert, Flum. There's more coming.</font>

107
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

108
00:08:52,630 --> 00:08:53,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gadhio.</font>

109
00:08:55,220 --> 00:08:57,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You came to help.</font>

110
00:08:57,270 --> 00:08:57,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

111
00:08:58,990 --> 00:09:01,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This girl named Sara asked me to.</font>

112
00:09:03,380 --> 00:09:04,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

113
00:09:05,590 --> 00:09:09,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sara's... alive?</font>

114
00:09:10,270 --> 00:09:11,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

115
00:09:11,660 --> 00:09:17,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Having thought she'd lost everything, 
Flum had been shrouded in despair,</i></font>

116
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:20,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but with those words, a ray of hope 
began to shine within her once again.</i></font>

117
00:09:23,330 --> 00:09:26,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have to go.</font>

118
00:09:37,700 --> 00:09:39,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Link up.</font>

119
00:09:39,380 --> 00:09:40,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Connection.</font>

120
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flum!</font>

121
00:09:47,390 --> 00:09:48,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get going!</font>

122
00:09:50,470 --> 00:09:53,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll handle this.</font>

123
00:09:59,830 --> 00:10:02,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck? You're a freak.</font>

124
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:04,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One of the Children?</font>

125
00:10:04,540 --> 00:10:08,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ink blabbed about that too?</font>

126
00:10:08,130 --> 00:10:09,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That useless nitwit.</font>

127
00:10:11,740 --> 00:10:13,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You spiral monster.</font>

128
00:10:14,340 --> 00:10:15,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prepare to die!</font>

129
00:10:16,470 --> 00:10:18,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right back at you, mister.</font>

130
00:10:18,810 --> 00:10:20,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Connection.</font>

131
00:10:21,190 --> 00:10:22,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just wait! I'll be right there...</i></font>

132
00:10:23,510 --> 00:10:24,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Milkit!</i></font>

133
00:10:25,230 --> 00:10:26,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ink!</i></font>

134
00:10:30,310 --> 00:10:31,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

135
00:10:31,730 --> 00:10:36,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The stable outside the yard has 
a hidden passage to the inside, huh?</font>

136
00:10:39,430 --> 00:10:40,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A Church lapdog?</font>

137
00:10:54,630 --> 00:10:57,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome, Flum Apricot,</font>

138
00:10:57,970 --> 00:11:01,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to Satils Francois's mansion!</font>

139
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:03,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where are Milkit and Ink?</font>

140
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:08,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Beats me. You should worry 
more about your own life.</font>

141
00:11:08,260 --> 00:11:10,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ha! You're the one who's gonna die!</font>

142
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:17,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sending your ass to the grave!</font>

143
00:11:36,400 --> 00:11:38,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's one bothersome body 
you've got there.</font>

144
00:11:40,130 --> 00:11:42,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could say the same to you.</font>

145
00:11:42,430 --> 00:11:46,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you get that in return 
for joining the Church of Origin?</font>

146
00:11:46,220 --> 00:11:47,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, that's right.</font>

147
00:11:47,870 --> 00:11:49,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't it great?</font>

148
00:11:50,910 --> 00:11:52,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And just for that,</font>

149
00:11:52,330 --> 00:11:53,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you sold out your buddies?</font>

150
00:11:54,090 --> 00:11:55,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had no other choice!</font>

151
00:11:55,990 --> 00:11:56,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're no different!</font>

152
00:11:57,220 --> 00:11:59,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you were faced with absolute power</font>

153
00:11:59,050 --> 00:12:01,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that no amount of money 
or influence could ever equal,</font>

154
00:12:01,620 --> 00:12:05,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a power that could even 
change the laws of the world,</font>

155
00:12:05,950 --> 00:12:07,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">even you...</font>

156
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:11,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">would make the same choice.</font>

157
00:12:27,370 --> 00:12:29,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's Satils Francois for you.</font>

158
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:35,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The mummy girl's former master 
has some nasty taste.</font>

159
00:12:36,310 --> 00:12:39,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Those tentacles will bat 
any regular attacks away.</i></font>

160
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:41,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In that case...</i></font>

161
00:12:45,780 --> 00:12:47,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Prana Shaker.</i></font>

162
00:12:51,100 --> 00:12:52,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Too bad!</font>

163
00:12:56,570 --> 00:12:58,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on! What's wrong?</font>

164
00:13:00,340 --> 00:13:01,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do what you always do,</font>

165
00:13:02,090 --> 00:13:06,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and show you've got the guts 
to take from me!</font>

166
00:13:08,310 --> 00:13:10,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gotcha,</font>

167
00:13:10,800 --> 00:13:13,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flum Apricot!</font>

168
00:13:14,740 --> 00:13:18,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With my buddies dead 
and my humanity gone...</font>

169
00:13:18,790 --> 00:13:22,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was forced to think about 
what I even had left!</font>

170
00:13:23,590 --> 00:13:27,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it looks like I can cross 
one last regret off that list!</font>

171
00:13:28,110 --> 00:13:31,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your life is mine, Flum!</font>

172
00:13:31,750 --> 00:13:37,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The lady told me not to kill you, 
but like I care about her orders!</font>

173
00:13:38,150 --> 00:13:41,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This will be the first step 
of my comeback.</font>

174
00:13:41,760 --> 00:13:43,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll rule the West District again.</font>

175
00:13:44,900 --> 00:13:46,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, no.</font>

176
00:13:46,100 --> 00:13:50,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take over the whole 
kingdom this time,</font>

177
00:13:50,340 --> 00:13:52,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with this power of mine!</font>

178
00:13:53,070 --> 00:13:57,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Create a clear vision in your mind 
and say the words that come naturally.</i></font>

179
00:13:58,860 --> 00:14:00,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rev...</font>

180
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:05,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Begging for your life? Not gonna help.</font>

181
00:14:06,610 --> 00:14:08,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reversal...</font>

182
00:14:19,910 --> 00:14:22,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you do, Flum?!</font>

183
00:14:25,220 --> 00:14:28,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh? The tentacles are rotting away?</i></font>

184
00:14:29,320 --> 00:14:33,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Flum had only pictured them 
loosening their grip on her.</i></font>

185
00:14:36,390 --> 00:14:37,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reversal!</font>

186
00:14:41,350 --> 00:14:44,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell? 
My power's supposed to be divine!</font>

187
00:14:45,190 --> 00:14:48,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't it supposed to be 
the great Origin's power?!</font>

188
00:14:51,520 --> 00:14:56,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what you get for relying 
on Origin's shady power!</font>

189
00:14:56,170 --> 00:15:00,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not letting some 
damn slave girl stop me!</font>

190
00:15:00,080 --> 00:15:01,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prana Shaker:</font>

191
00:15:02,010 --> 00:15:03,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reversal!</font>

192
00:15:11,500 --> 00:15:16,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I see. So even Origin's power 
can be reversed.</i></font>

193
00:15:19,870 --> 00:15:21,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's a voice of corruption...</i></font>

194
00:15:21,820 --> 00:15:24,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Flum Apricot.</i></font>

195
00:15:24,540 --> 00:15:30,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You mustn't listen 
to the voice of corruption.</i></font>

196
00:15:30,370 --> 00:15:32,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Flum Apricot.</i></font>

197
00:15:33,200 --> 00:15:36,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}You mustn't look its way.</i></font>

198
00:15:33,260 --> 00:15:37,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn, those voices again. 
That lady and Origin...</font>

199
00:15:38,380 --> 00:15:40,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Flum Apricot.</i></font>

200
00:15:40,900 --> 00:15:43,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are they so scared of this slave girl?</font>

201
00:15:43,540 --> 00:15:45,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you mumbling about?</font>

202
00:15:45,570 --> 00:15:46,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Making excuses for losing?</font>

203
00:15:47,690 --> 00:15:50,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You think you've already won?</font>

204
00:15:50,060 --> 00:15:52,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't have a clue.</font>

205
00:15:52,910 --> 00:15:55,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have no idea what my true ability is.</font>

206
00:15:56,310 --> 00:15:59,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is my very own power, 
granted to me by Origin.</font>

207
00:15:59,520 --> 00:16:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One that I can use thanks to the 
dark crystal embedded in me!</font>

208
00:16:03,220 --> 00:16:03,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

209
00:16:05,230 --> 00:16:07,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ink's heart isn't beating.</font>

210
00:16:08,270 --> 00:16:10,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There must be something 
acting as its replacement.</font>

211
00:16:11,650 --> 00:16:15,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Has Ink had a dark crystal 
embedded in her, too?</i></font>

212
00:16:15,580 --> 00:16:20,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The power of the core will 
slaughter all that defy me!</font>

213
00:16:21,130 --> 00:16:22,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The core?</font>

214
00:16:23,460 --> 00:16:25,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The core broke?</font>

215
00:16:32,660 --> 00:16:35,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More! Take over her body!</font>

216
00:16:35,620 --> 00:16:38,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Turn into an ugly lump of flesh</font>

217
00:16:38,530 --> 00:16:41,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and die, Flum!</font>

218
00:16:45,580 --> 00:16:47,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, next.</font>

219
00:16:48,910 --> 00:16:52,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ink didn't know she was 
popping out eyeballs</i></font>

220
00:16:52,960 --> 00:16:54,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>or attacking people.</i></font>

221
00:16:55,830 --> 00:16:58,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This power must be...</i></font>

222
00:16:59,110 --> 00:17:02,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong? Why'd you all stop?</font>

223
00:17:02,270 --> 00:17:04,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Defend me like you always do!</font>

224
00:17:04,860 --> 00:17:05,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make me...</font>

225
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:06,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not happening.</font>

226
00:17:06,930 --> 00:17:07,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

227
00:17:08,190 --> 00:17:10,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's Ink's power.</font>

228
00:17:10,510 --> 00:17:14,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A power she uses to protect her friends, 
family, and those dear to her.</font>

229
00:17:14,810 --> 00:17:17,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bah! This power is mine!</font>

230
00:17:17,310 --> 00:17:19,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what they told me, too!</font>

231
00:17:19,680 --> 00:17:21,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were tricked.</font>

232
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:23,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because that made you 
easier to manipulate.</font>

233
00:17:24,520 --> 00:17:26,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem to be in a spot of bother.</font>

234
00:17:27,180 --> 00:17:29,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm with the Church.</font>

235
00:17:30,350 --> 00:17:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm willing to lend you aid.</font>

236
00:17:33,950 --> 00:17:37,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"I wouldn't put it past 
that bitch," he thought.</i></font>

237
00:17:37,200 --> 00:17:41,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And the moment he followed up with, 
"And I'd fall for it as I am now, too..."</i></font>

238
00:17:41,070 --> 00:17:44,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We want to be linked. Let's connect.</i></font>

239
00:17:45,500 --> 00:17:48,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It can't be! This is <i>my</i> power!</font>

240
00:17:49,150 --> 00:17:51,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Defend me!</font>

241
00:17:51,660 --> 00:17:54,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I said all those awful things to Ink,</i></font>

242
00:17:54,810 --> 00:17:58,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and she's still protecting me.</i></font>

243
00:18:00,940 --> 00:18:03,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have to apologize to her.</i></font>

244
00:18:04,100 --> 00:18:05,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me. Where is Ink?</font>

245
00:18:11,790 --> 00:18:13,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It makes no sense!</font>

246
00:18:13,400 --> 00:18:16,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could I lose to a slave like you?</font>

247
00:18:16,870 --> 00:18:18,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a natural-born ruler!</font>

248
00:18:18,430 --> 00:18:22,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After we lost our nobility, 
I was forced to struggle in the slums...</font>

249
00:18:23,210 --> 00:18:29,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I clawed my way up with my own hands! 
I'm a champion of the people!</font>

250
00:18:29,660 --> 00:18:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I spent years building my empire,</font>

251
00:18:33,000 --> 00:18:37,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and some heartless monsters show up 
outta nowhere to destroy it all?</font>

252
00:18:38,220 --> 00:18:42,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This isn't right! It can't be right!</font>

253
00:18:42,680 --> 00:18:46,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Screw the Church. Screw the Children.</font>

254
00:18:46,340 --> 00:18:48,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Screw Origin!</font>

255
00:18:48,390 --> 00:18:49,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fuck it all!</font>

256
00:18:49,770 --> 00:18:51,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fuck you!</font>

257
00:18:55,340 --> 00:18:59,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell? How could I lose?</font>

258
00:19:01,140 --> 00:19:02,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't give a shit!</font>

259
00:19:03,470 --> 00:19:08,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All my buddies who I used to 
goof off with are dead too.</font>

260
00:19:08,940 --> 00:19:11,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, what do you think I'm supposed to do?</font>

261
00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:13,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the one who abandoned them.</font>

262
00:19:14,170 --> 00:19:17,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They believed in you and followed you.</font>

263
00:19:17,760 --> 00:19:20,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you took away their wills 
and turned them into pawns.</font>

264
00:19:21,700 --> 00:19:24,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have no right to whine 
and moan after what you did.</font>

265
00:19:24,670 --> 00:19:27,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you getting mad at me?</font>

266
00:19:27,290 --> 00:19:31,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, are you playing hero again, 
Miss Goody Two-Shoes?</font>

267
00:19:31,600 --> 00:19:35,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were able to be of use to me. 
They should be happy about that.</font>

268
00:19:35,700 --> 00:19:38,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, keep telling yourself that.</font>

269
00:19:38,430 --> 00:19:41,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep trying to run away from the fact 
that you betrayed your friends.</font>

270
00:19:41,440 --> 00:19:44,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't ask for any of this 
either, you know.</font>

271
00:19:45,380 --> 00:19:49,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that punk Kahnis hadn't turned on me...</font>

272
00:19:50,470 --> 00:19:52,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with that look?</font>

273
00:19:52,250 --> 00:19:55,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you were forced to choose between 
your life and your friendships...</font>

274
00:19:56,030 --> 00:20:00,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you had to choose one or the other, 
you'd make the same choice!</font>

275
00:20:00,640 --> 00:20:01,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not like you.</font>

276
00:20:02,730 --> 00:20:06,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd never sacrifice the people 
near and dear to me.</font>

277
00:20:06,790 --> 00:20:08,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enough of your idealistic nonsense!</font>

278
00:20:08,880 --> 00:20:12,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were sold out by your friends, too! 
Into slavery, even!</font>

279
00:20:12,660 --> 00:20:16,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were this close to ending up like me!</font>

280
00:20:19,550 --> 00:20:22,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you think that'd make me 
take pity on you?</font>

281
00:20:24,450 --> 00:20:26,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't expect to be coddled. 
It's disgusting.</font>

282
00:20:27,550 --> 00:20:31,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me, coddled? You're kidding me.</font>

283
00:20:32,280 --> 00:20:34,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Dein had lost everything—</i></font>

284
00:20:34,300 --> 00:20:37,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>his power, his fame, his friends, 
and his place in the world.</i></font>

285
00:20:37,290 --> 00:20:42,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All he had left was his pointless ego and 
his obsession with the girl before him.</i></font>

286
00:20:42,730 --> 00:20:45,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And now, even his ego was in tatters.</i></font>

287
00:20:46,820 --> 00:20:49,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No... No!</font>

288
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:51,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What drove me was...</font>

289
00:20:51,420 --> 00:20:58,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We want to be linked. Let's connect.</i></font>

290
00:20:55,070 --> 00:20:57,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go away! Stay out of my head!</font>

291
00:20:58,820 --> 00:21:00,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

292
00:20:59,990 --> 00:21:05,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We want to be linked. Let's connect.</i></font>

293
00:21:00,130 --> 00:21:02,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I decide what I do!</font>

294
00:21:05,230 --> 00:21:07,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on here?</font>

295
00:21:07,610 --> 00:21:08,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll kill...</font>

296
00:21:08,960 --> 00:21:10,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will kill you.</font>

297
00:21:12,620 --> 00:21:14,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flum.</font>

298
00:21:14,750 --> 00:21:17,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If only you hadn't shown up,</font>

299
00:21:17,430 --> 00:21:20,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">my dream would...</font>

300
00:21:22,560 --> 00:21:25,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Dein did say he had 
a core embedded in him.</i></font>

301
00:21:26,850 --> 00:21:27,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In that case...</i></font>

302
00:21:28,350 --> 00:21:32,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can put him down for good!</font>

303
00:21:32,870 --> 00:21:34,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reversal!</font>

304
00:21:54,550 --> 00:21:59,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who knows how many people 
you've sacrificed for your dream?</font>

305
00:22:01,210 --> 00:22:03,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Regret the choices that 
led you here as you die.</font>

306
00:22:05,550 --> 00:22:10,270
<font face="Times New Roman" size="14"><b>{\an9}Translation: Sriram Gurunathan</b></font>

307
00:22:10,560 --> 00:22:15,270
<font face="Times New Roman" size="14"><b>{\an9}Subtitle Editing: Geoff Mazzolini

Subtitle Timing: Krzysztof Kunc</b></font>

308
00:22:15,570 --> 00:22:20,280
<font face="Times New Roman" size="14"><b>{\an9}Quality Check: Riley Dalton

Translation Check: Rei Miyasaka</b></font>

309
00:23:37,690 --> 00:23:40,020
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}THE END AND THE BEGINNING</b></font>

